    "This technique uses plant diseases and pests to construct the image scheme and choose the appropriate light source and shooting angle.",
    "This method ensures that images have uniform lighting.",
    "Designed imaging systems can reduce the complexity of constructing a standard algorithm but lead to an increase in application costs.",
    "It is sometimes difficult to expect standard algorithms to completely remove scene changes from recognized results to work in a natural environment (Dell' Aquila 2009).",
